## Architecture Principles

### Multi-Tenancy
- **Strategy**: Single database, shared schema
- **Isolation**: All tables have `StationId` foreign key
- **Queries**: Global filter via EF Core query filters
- **Owner View**: Aggregates data across all owned stations

### Clean Architecture (Backend)

The backend uses **Clean Architecture** with 4 separate .NET projects. Dependencies flow inward — inner layers never reference outer layers.

| Project | Role | Depends On |
|:--|:--|:--|
| **FuelFlow.Domain** | Entities, enums, business rules (pure C#, zero packages) | Nothing |
| **FuelFlow.Application** | Commands, Queries, interfaces, DTOs, validators, Result type | Domain |
| **FuelFlow.Infrastructure** | Command/Query handlers, EF Core, repos, JWT, external services | Application, Domain |
| **FuelFlow.Api** | Controllers, Program.cs (composition root) | Application, Infrastructure |

```
FuelFlow.Domain/         # Entities/, Enums/, Common/
FuelFlow.Application/    # Features/*/Commands/, Features/*/Queries/, Interfaces/, DTOs/, Validators/, Common/
FuelFlow.Infrastructure/ # Features/*/Commands/, Features/*/Queries/, Data/, Repositories/, Services/
FuelFlow.Api/            # Controllers/, Middleware/, Program.cs
```

**CQRS + MediatR:**
- Controllers send Commands/Queries via `IMediator.Send()` — never call handlers directly
- Commands = state-changing operations (e.g., `RegisterCommand`, `LoginCommand`)
- Queries = read-only operations (e.g., `GetCurrentUserQuery`)
- Handlers live in Infrastructure, implement `IRequestHandler<TRequest, TResponse>`
- Handlers return `Result<T>` for explicit success/failure

**Key rules:**
- Domain has NO NuGet packages — pure C# only
- Entities are POCOs — no EF Core attributes, no `[Table]` or `[Column]`
- EF Core mapping done via Fluent API in Infrastructure (Configurations/)
- Interfaces defined in Application, implemented in Infrastructure
- Api is the composition root — the only project that knows about all layers

**Frontend** (`fuel-flow-web/`):
```
src/
  ├── routes/          # TanStack Router file-based routes
  ├── components/
  │   ├── ui/         # Shadcn components
  │   ├── forms/      # Form components
  │   └── layout/     # Shell, sidebar, header
  ├── hooks/
  │   ├── useAuth.ts
  │   └── queries/    # TanStack Query hooks
  ├── lib/
  │   ├── api.ts      # Axios/fetch config
  │   ├── utils.ts
  │   └── validators.ts # Zod schemas
  ├── stores/         # Zustand stores
  └── locales/        # i18n (en.json, ur.json)
```

